{"id":2632,"date":"2025-05-13T15:57:33","date_gmt":"2025-05-13T08:57:33","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=2632"},"modified":"2025-06-09T10:21:26","modified_gmt":"2025-06-09T03:21:26","slug":"da-kho-nen-dung-gi","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/xu-huong\/da-kho-nen-dung-gi\/","title":{"rendered":"Da kh\u00f4 n\u00ean d\u00f9ng g\u00ec ch\u1ed1ng l\u00e3o ho\u00e1 da t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><b><i>Da kh\u00f4 n\u00ean d\u00f9ng g\u00ec<\/i><\/b><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">? Khi l\u00e0n da n\u00e0y lu\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng da kh\u00f4 bong tr\u00f3c hay th\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1eb7p nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 l\u00e3o ho\u00e1. Da kh\u00f4 c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u0103m s\u00f3c \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng n\u00e0y. V\u1eady v\u00ec sao da m\u1eb7t l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4? T\u1ea1i sao da kh\u00f4 l\u1ea1i th\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1ecb l\u00e3o ho\u00e1 da d\u1ec5 h\u01a1n. C\u00f9ng GSC t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u chi ti\u1ebft v\u1ec1 c\u00e1ch nh\u1eadn bi\u1ebft da kh\u00f4 v\u00e0 bi\u1ebft da kh\u00f4 n\u00ean d\u00f9ng g\u00ec trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y nh\u00e9!<\/span><\/i><\/p>\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"da-kho-nen-dung-gi-tai-sao-da-mat-lai-kho\"><\/span><b>Da kh\u00f4 n\u00ean d\u00f9ng g\u00ec? T\u1ea1i sao da m\u1eb7t l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><strong>Da kh\u00f4 n\u00ean d\u00f9ng g\u00ec<\/strong> v\u00e0 t\u1ea1i sao da m\u1eb7t l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4 nh\u1ec9? V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 th\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb nhi\u1ec1u nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n kh\u00e1c nhau, nh\u1eefng nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ch\u00ednh s\u1ebd l\u00e0: Tu\u1ed5i t\u00e1c, di truy\u1ec1n, b\u1ec7nh l\u00fd.\u00a0 Da kh\u00f4 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 do y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 di truy\u1ec1n m\u00e0 c\u00f2n b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng b\u1edfi nhi\u1ec1u nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n kh\u00e1c nhau:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2636\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2636\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-2636 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/da-kho-nen-dung-gi-tot.webp\" alt=\"T\u1ea1i sao da m\u1eb7t l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/da-kho-nen-dung-gi-tot.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/da-kho-nen-dung-gi-tot-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/da-kho-nen-dung-gi-tot-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/da-kho-nen-dung-gi-tot-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2636\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>T\u1ea1i sao da m\u1eb7t l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Thi\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m: L\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc trong da kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 g\u00e2y t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng kh\u00f4 r\u00e1p, bong tr\u00f3c.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u00e1c nh\u00e2n m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng: Th\u1eddi ti\u1ebft hanh kh\u00f4, ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac v\u1edbi \u00e1nh n\u1eafng m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi, \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00f2a.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p: C\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t c\u00f3 t\u00ednh ki\u1ec1m cao( pH cao) ho\u1eb7c ch\u1ee9a c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n t\u1ea9y r\u1eeda m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Thi\u1ebfu d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t: C\u00e1c vitamin v\u00e0 kho\u00e1ng ch\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u01b0 vitamin E, C, omega-3.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Th\u00f3i quen sinh ho\u1ea1t: U\u1ed1ng \u00edt n\u01b0\u1edbc, th\u1ee9c khuya, stress.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"da-kho-thuong-co-dac-diem-ra-sao\"><\/span><b>Da kh\u00f4 th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 \u0111\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m ra sao?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chia l\u00e0m l\u00e0m nhi\u1ec1u lo\u1ea1i kh\u00e1c nhau nh\u01b0 da d\u1ea7u, da h\u1ed7 h\u1ee3p, nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m hay da kh\u00f4. Ch\u1ecb em s\u1edf h\u1eefu l\u00e0n da kh\u00f4 th\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u201cTuy\u1ebfn b\u00e3 nh\u1eddn d\u01b0\u1edbi da ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t\u201d. D\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c d\u1ea7u tr\u00ean b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t da ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ebd k\u00e9m h\u01a1n b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng. Vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn cho da kh\u00f4 lu\u00f4n trong t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng kh\u00f4 r\u00e1p, bong ho\u1eb7c tr\u00f3c nh\u1eb9.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2635\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2635\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-2635 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/da-kho-nen-dung-gi-tot-nhat.webp\" alt=\"Da kh\u00f4 th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 \u0111\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m ra sao\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/da-kho-nen-dung-gi-tot-nhat.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/da-kho-nen-dung-gi-tot-nhat-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/da-kho-nen-dung-gi-tot-nhat-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/da-kho-nen-dung-gi-tot-nhat-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2635\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>Da kh\u00f4 n\u00ean d\u00f9ng g\u00ec &#8211; Da kh\u00f4 th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 \u0111\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m ra sao<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u00e0n da c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u1eb7p t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng kh\u00f4 to\u00e0n th\u00e2n ho\u1eb7c ch\u1ec9 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u1edf nh\u1eefng v\u00f9ng nh\u01b0 m\u1eb7t, c\u00e1nh tay, khu\u1ef7u tay, b\u00e0n tay ho\u1eb7c ch\u00e2n. T\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng da kh\u00f4 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf c\u1ea3 nam v\u00e0 n\u1eef, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i. Da m\u1eb7t kh\u00f4 th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u nh\u01b0:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da x\u1ec9n m\u00e0u: N\u1ebfu tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p da thi\u1ebfu s\u00e1ng ho\u1eb7c c\u0103ng b\u00f3ng c\u0169ng l\u00e0 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u da \u0111ang kh\u00f4<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da c\u00f3 c\u00e1c m\u1ea3ng kh\u00f4, bong tr\u00f3c: Da kh\u00f4 th\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1ecb kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu, da \u0111\u1ecf v\u00e0 g\u00e2y m\u1ea5t c\u1ea3m quan<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u1ea7u ti\u1ebft ra \u00edt h\u01a1n: V\u1edbi da kh\u00f4, khi l\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u1ea7u ti\u1ebft ra \u00edt h\u01a1n, da th\u01b0\u1eddng thi\u1ebfu v\u1ebb t\u01b0\u01a1i t\u1eafn t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb k\u00edch \u1ee9ng, ng\u1ee9a v\u00e0 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u00e1c n\u1ebfp nh\u0103n s\u1edbm tr\u00ean da<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"2-dau-hieu-nhan-biet-da-kho-chuan-nhat-tu-chuyen-gia\"><\/span><b>2 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u nh\u00e2n bi\u1ebft da kh\u00f4 chu\u1ea9n nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb chuy\u00ean gia<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"nhan-biet-dua-vao-quan-sat\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Nh\u1eadn bi\u1ebft d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o quan s\u00e1t<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Nh\u1eadn bi\u1ebft da kh\u00f4 kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f3, ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n b\u1ea1n quan s\u00e1t l\u00e0n da c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. N\u1ebfu g\u1eb7p nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u sau, r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 da b\u1ea1n \u0111ang thi\u1ebfu \u1ea9m v\u00e0 c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u0103m s\u00f3c ngay:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c da b\u1ecb k\u00e9o c\u0103ng: Da th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c c\u0103ng, kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 sau khi r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ng\u1ee9a ng\u00e1y, kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu: Thi\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m khi\u1ebfn da d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb k\u00edch \u1ee9ng, g\u00e2y c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c ng\u1ee9a.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t da tr\u1edf n\u00ean th\u00f4 v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec1u: Da m\u1ea5t \u0111i s\u1ef1 m\u1ec1m m\u1ea1i, tr\u1edf n\u00ean kh\u00f4 v\u00e0 x\u1ec9n m\u00e0u do thi\u1ebfu n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n v\u1ea3y tr\u1eafng: N\u1ebfu t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng kh\u00f4 k\u00e9o d\u00e0i, da c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u00e1c m\u1ea3ng v\u1ea3y tr\u1eafng bong tr\u00f3c.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">N\u1ebfp nh\u0103n li ti: Thi\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m l\u00e0m suy gi\u1ea3m collagen v\u00e0 elastin, khi\u1ebfn da nhanh l\u00e3o h\u00f3a v\u00e0 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u00e1c n\u1ebfp nh\u0103n nh\u1ecf.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 tr\u00ean, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 quy tr\u00ecnh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 l\u00e0n da kh\u1ecfi t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng kh\u00f4 c\u0103ng v\u00e0 l\u00e3o h\u00f3a s\u1edbm.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2633\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2633\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-2633 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/da-kho-nen-dung-gi-chuyen-gia.webp\" alt=\"d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u nh\u00e2n bi\u1ebft da kh\u00f4 chu\u1ea9n nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb chuy\u00ean gia\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/da-kho-nen-dung-gi-chuyen-gia.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/da-kho-nen-dung-gi-chuyen-gia-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/da-kho-nen-dung-gi-chuyen-gia-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/da-kho-nen-dung-gi-chuyen-gia-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2633\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u nh\u00e2n bi\u1ebft da kh\u00f4 chu\u1ea9n nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb chuy\u00ean gia<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"dua-vao-giay-tham-dau\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u1ef1a v\u00e0o gi\u1ea5y th\u1ea5m d\u1ea7u<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng da kh\u00f4 l\u00e0 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng gi\u1ea5y th\u1ea5m d\u1ea7u. C\u00e1c b\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n nh\u01b0 sau:<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 1: Da kh\u00f4 n\u00ean d\u00f9ng g\u00ec &#8211; L\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ec3 lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n v\u00e0 d\u1ea7u th\u1eeba.<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 2: N\u1ebfu c\u00f3, h\u00e3y thoa m\u1ed9t l\u1edbp toner nh\u1eb9, sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee3i kho\u1ea3ng 1-2 gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ec3 da tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean.<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 3: C\u1eaft gi\u1ea5y th\u1ea5m d\u1ea7u th\u00e0nh 6-8 mi\u1ebfng nh\u1ecf, \u00e1p nh\u1eb9 l\u00ean tr\u00e1n, m\u0169i, hai g\u00f2 m\u00e1 v\u00e0 c\u1eb1m. Gi\u1eef kho\u1ea3ng 5 ph\u00fat r\u1ed3i ki\u1ec3m tra k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3.<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 4: Quan s\u00e1t gi\u1ea5y th\u1ea5m d\u1ea7u:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">N\u1ebfu gi\u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng th\u1ea5m ho\u1eb7c ch\u1ec9 th\u1ea5m m\u1ed9t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u1ea7u r\u1ea5t \u00edt \u2192 Da b\u1ea1n thu\u1ed9c nh\u00f3m da kh\u00f4.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">N\u1ebfu gi\u1ea5y th\u1ea5m nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea7u, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf v\u00f9ng ch\u1eef T \u2192 Da c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thu\u1ed9c nh\u00f3m da d\u1ea7u ho\u1eb7c h\u1ed7n h\u1ee3p.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da kh\u00f4 kh\u00f4ng ti\u1ebft nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea7u n\u00ean gi\u1ea5y th\u1ea5m d\u1ea7u s\u1ebd g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 v\u1ebft d\u1ea7u. Khi soi g\u01b0\u01a1ng, b\u1ea1n c\u0169ng s\u1ebd th\u1ea5y da c\u00f3 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u s\u1ea7n s\u00f9i, n\u1ee9t n\u1ebb nh\u1eb9. N\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y da m\u00ecnh thu\u1ed9c lo\u1ea1i da kh\u00f4, h\u00e3y ch\u00fa \u00fd c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m v\u00e0 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e0n h\u1ed3i v\u00e0 kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh nh\u00e9!<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cac-buoc-skincare-cho-da-kho-chuan-khoa-hoc-tai-nha\"><\/span><b>C\u00e1c b\u01b0\u1edbc skincare cho da kh\u00f4 chu\u1ea9n khoa h\u1ecdc t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u00e0n da kh\u00f4 c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c <\/span><b>ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da kh\u00f4 <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 m\u1ecbn m\u00e0ng. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 quy tr\u00ecnh skincare chu\u1ea9n khoa h\u1ecdc d\u00e0nh cho da kh\u00f4:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2634\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2634\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-2634 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/da-kho-nen-dung-gi-routine.webp\" alt=\"C\u00e1c b\u01b0\u1edbc skincare cho da kh\u00f4 chu\u1ea9n khoa h\u1ecdc t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/da-kho-nen-dung-gi-routine.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/da-kho-nen-dung-gi-routine-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/da-kho-nen-dung-gi-routine-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/da-kho-nen-dung-gi-routine-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2634\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>C\u00e1c b\u01b0\u1edbc skincare cho da kh\u00f4 chu\u1ea9n khoa h\u1ecdc t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"buoc-1-tay-trang-ki\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 1: T\u1ea9y trang k\u0129<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u1ea9y trang l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean thi\u1ebft y\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch da, lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n, d\u1ea7u nh\u1eddn v\u00e0 l\u1edbp trang \u0111i\u1ec3m.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi da kh\u00f4, n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m t\u1ea9y trang d\u1ea1ng d\u1ea7u ho\u1eb7c n\u01b0\u1edbc micellar nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da kh\u1ecfi kh\u00f4 r\u00e1t.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng: D\u1ea7u t\u1ea9y trang gi\u00fap l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch s\u00e2u, lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf c\u1eb7n b\u1ea9n trong l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng, c\u00f2n n\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1ea9y trang ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi l\u00e0n da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"buoc-2-su-dung-sua-rua-mat-nhe-nhang\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 2: S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">R\u1eeda m\u1eb7t gi\u00fap lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf c\u00e1c t\u1ea1p ch\u1ea5t c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i tr\u00ean da m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m kh\u00f4 da ho\u1eb7c l\u00e0m m\u1ea5t \u0111i \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u01b0u \u00fd: Tr\u00e1nh s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ea9y r\u1eeda cao, \u01b0u ti\u00ean s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 pH kho\u1ea3ng 5.5 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng da.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"buoc-3-can-bang-do-ph-toner\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 3: C\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9 pH( Toner)<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Toner gi\u00fap c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m t\u1ee9c th\u00ec, l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu v\u00e0 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9 pH cho da.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn: Toner ch\u1ee9a Hyaluronic Acid, Ceramides gi\u00fap duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m. Ho\u1eb7c chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean nh\u01b0 c\u00e2y ph\u1ec9, tr\u00e0m tr\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu da.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"buoc-4-da-kho-nen-dung-gi-%e2%80%93-su-dung-them-mat-na\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 4: Da kh\u00f4 n\u00ean d\u00f9ng g\u00ec &#8211; S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng th\u00eam m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da kh\u00f4 n\u00ean d\u00f9ng g\u00ec ngo\u00e0i b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da nh\u01b0 toner hay serum? M\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch nhanh ch\u00f3ng b\u1ed5 sung d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t cho da kh\u00f4. \u01afu ti\u00ean l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 c\u1ea5p n\u01b0\u1edbc cho da.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2605\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2605\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-2605 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/cach-su-dung-mat-na.webp\" alt=\"C\u00e1c b\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 gel \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/cach-su-dung-mat-na.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/cach-su-dung-mat-na-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/cach-su-dung-mat-na-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/cach-su-dung-mat-na-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2605\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>Da kh\u00f4 n\u00ean d\u00f9ng g\u00ec &#8211; C\u00e1c b\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 gel \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">G\u1ee3i \u00fd:\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 gi\u1ea5y c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m 2-3 l\u1ea7n\/tu\u1ea7n gi\u00fap da m\u1ec1m m\u1ecbn, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t v\u00e0o m\u00f9a l\u1ea1nh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u0103ng t\u1ea7n su\u1ea5t s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1eb7t n\u1ea1 d\u1ea1ng gel c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng t\u1ea7n su\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n, m\u1ec1m m\u1ecbn v\u00e0 c\u0103ng b\u00f3ng da t\u1ee9c th\u00ec<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"buoc-5-bo-sung-them-serumtinh-chat\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 5: B\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam serum\/tinh ch\u1ea5t<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da kh\u00f4 n\u00ean d\u00f9ng g\u00ec &#8211; Serum ch\u1ee9a d\u1ea7u d\u01b0\u1ee1ng gi\u00fap nu\u00f4i d\u01b0\u1ee1ng da t\u1eeb s\u00e2u b\u00ean trong.<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn: Serum c\u00f3 k\u1ebft c\u1ea5u ph\u00e2n t\u1ea7ng, k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 d\u1ea7u, gi\u00fap kh\u00f3a \u1ea9m v\u00e0 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00e1ch d\u00f9ng: L\u1eafc nh\u1eb9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ec3 hai t\u1ea7ng h\u00f2a quy\u1ec7n, thoa \u0111\u1ec1u v\u00e0 v\u1ed7 nh\u1eb9 \u0111\u1ec3 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t th\u1ea9m th\u1ea5u.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"buoc-6-khoa-am-bang-kem-duong\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u01b0\u1edbc 6: Kho\u00e1 \u1ea9m b\u1eb1ng kem d\u01b0\u1ee1ng<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><b>C\u1ea5p \u1ea9m cho da kh\u00f4<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch n\u00e0o? Kem d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m gi\u00fap ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba m\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da.<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n n\u00ean c\u00f3: Hyaluronic Acid, Collagen, Vitamin E, d\u1ea7u Jojoba, ceramide c\u00e1c chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean gi\u00fap kh\u00f3a \u1ea9m, l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu da kh\u00f4, h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf bong tr\u00f3c.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u01b0u \u00fd: Ch\u1ecdn s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y b\u00edt t\u1eafc l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng (Non-comedogenic) \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"-buoc-7-thoa-kem-chong-nang\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u00a0B\u01b0\u1edbc 7: Thoa kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng v\u1eadt l\u00fd l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 quan tr\u1ecdng, gi\u00fap ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba t\u00e1c h\u1ea1i t\u1eeb tia UV.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn: N\u00ean ch\u1ecdn s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m nh\u01b0 Glycerin v\u00e0 Ceramides \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef cho da lu\u00f4n \u1ea9m m\u1ecbn.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u1ea1ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p: Kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng d\u1ea1ng gel ho\u1eb7c x\u1ecbt s\u1ebd c\u1ea5p n\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1ed1t, kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c nh\u1eddn d\u00ednh.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"ket-luan\"><\/span><b>K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><strong>Da kh\u00f4 n\u00ean d\u00f9ng g\u00ec<\/strong>? Qua b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y c\u00e1c n\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch ch\u1ecdn s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p cho l\u00e0n da kh\u00f4. \u0110\u1eebng qu\u00ean truy c\u1eadp GSC \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u th\u00eam v\u1ec1 da kh\u00f4 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng da kh\u00e1c nh\u00e9. Ch\u00fac n\u00e0ng m\u00e3i xinh!<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Da kh\u00f4 n\u00ean d\u00f9ng g\u00ec? Khi l\u00e0n da n\u00e0y lu\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng da kh\u00f4 bong tr\u00f3c hay th\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1eb7p nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 l\u00e3o ho\u00e1.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":7,"featured_media":2636,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[13],"tags":[12,8],"class_list":["post-2632","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-xu-huong","tag-lam-dep-da","tag-new"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2632","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/7"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=2632"}],"version-history":[{"count":7,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2632\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":3989,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2632\/revisions\/3989"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/2636"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=2632"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=2632"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=2632"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}